snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 Character Guide | Terry
snippet.description:
You're gonna be okay after watching Terry's Character Guide!

The Legendary Hungry Wolf excels in both offense and defense and is a leader of the pack when it comes to special moves.

Terry joins the fight on September 24!
